description: Labour's Health Secretary, Wes Streeting said a planned clinical trial by NHS England would go ahead. The ban would then be reviewed in 2027 in the light of any new evidence that emerged.
title: MAIL ON SUNDAY COMMENT: Puberty blocker trial turns children into crash-test dummies
